{
  "sections": {
    "gp_section_565679898874610898": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "7153b2d77c0342671415cbadbaaa1421decaabb1e53807feaf033eec1087859a_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg0znNmAU8T_text": "<p><strong>No more stiffness that limits how you move or how you live.</strong></p>",
        "gg3GwCpV-GT_text": "<p><strong>No more relying on painkillers to get through the day.</strong></p>",
        "gg5A_s7vPft_text": "<p>After just a few uses, you can expect to feel muscles loosen, tension fade, and a renewed sense of energy.</p>",
        "gg6lqX8ncBw_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Backed by Clinical Research",
        "gg986IODh90_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-f5b26110-2655-434f-8ff3-f12bd892c75b.png",
        "gg9L3EDUCMV_text": "Find Lasting Relief With SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager",
        "ggGQXnMY5zT_text": "Find Lasting Relief With SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager",
        "ggOLny2Lf9H_text": "<p><strong>No more costly therapy appointments eating up your time and money.</strong></p>",
        "ggTX3oVSncW_text": "<p>In a randomized, double-blind clinical trial*, home-based NMES therapy led to significant improvements in pain relief and physical function over a 12-week period, compared to placebo treatments. This technology is trusted by physical therapists, rehabilitation clinics, and sports medicine professionals worldwide.</p>",
        "ggYhZQDCRPW_text": "<p>Just attach the SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager, set your intensity, and let it help your body heal - one 15-minute session at a time.</p>",
        "ggcllM8jPEK_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#3C89F1;\"><u>*</u></span><a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35514364/\"><span style=\"color:#3C89F1;\"><u>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35514364/</u></span></a></p>",
        "ggiVlsgDWSA_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager isn't just another gadget - it's grounded in real science. Neuromuscular Electrical Stimulation (NMES), the core technology behind our device, has been shown to reduce pain, stiffness, and improve joint function in clinical settings.</p>",
        "ggihBBrHnWy_text": "<p><strong>The SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager is quickly becoming a go-to solution for people tired of living with back, neck, and muscle pain.</strong></p>",
        "ggihisY810h_text": "Professionally Designed &amp; Backed by Clinical Research",
        "ggxdYnCiZ0G_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-138ee5ed-335c-4d74-bc21-d895b21b2cdf.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-565679898874610898"
    },
    "gp_section_565679898874676434": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "a7cab03c40e89f2123ebecafd391d3062b04b9347247aef44a783c2c8ee4ec8e_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Not at all. It’s a one-button system. Just attach the pad, press to turn it on, choose your mode, and relax. It’s fully wireless and rechargeable for simple, hands-free relief.</p>",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Yes! It’s designed for regular, safe use. In fact, we recommend using it daily for 15 minutes to see the best results over time. It’s drug-free, non-invasive, and gentle on your body.</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager is designed to help with a wide range of muscle and joint pain, including back, neck, shoulder, and leg discomfort. It works by targeting the underlying muscle tension and nerve irritation, not just masking the symptoms.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Unlike basic TENS devices that only stimulate nerves, NMES (Neuromuscular Electrical Stimulation) works deeper by also engaging your muscles. This helps reduce spasms, improve circulation, and support long-term healing - not just temporary numbness.</p>",
        "ggSrdFTGGTA_text": "<p>We offer a 90-day risk-free trial. If you don’t experience the relief you’re looking for, simply return it for a full refund - no questions asked.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>Many users report feeling noticeable relief within the first few sessions. For deeper pain or chronic conditions, consistent daily use helps build results over time as your body starts to recover.</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Will this work for my type of pain?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>What’s the difference between this and a TENS unit?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>Is it safe to use every day?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Do I need to be tech-savvy to use it?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>How long until I feel relief?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>What if it doesn’t work for me?</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-565679898874676434"
    },
    "gp_section_565679898874741970": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f3ff61a06dd3548a1c6cb8bce66b60f51b968b6685413572f6545a2f752628de_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg-AQS21-G0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-d0d341ec-69b6-4911-8671-be26ce751907.png",
        "gg9sfrUDNiv_text": "Heal, Move, and Live Better - Without the Struggle",
        "ggFoLsfJU5j_text": "<p>The SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager works by sending safe, gentle electrical pulses deep into your muscles, helping them relax, improving blood flow, and calming irritated nerves.</p>",
        "ggLpXZltW4C_text": "<p>Just place it on the painful area, select your intensity level, and relax. It’s hands-free, effortless, and fits easily into your daily routine</p>",
        "ggNDYVqN7Gc_text": "Heal, Move, and Live Better - Without the Struggle",
        "ggNxAHEd9SQ_text": "<p>This isn’t about numbing your pain - it’s about helping your body recover naturally, restoring strength and flexibility where you need it most.</p>",
        "ggd9w5iVAlN_text": "<p>And the best part? The more consistently you use it, the better you’ll feel: less pain, more freedom to move, and a stronger, healthier body for the long run.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-565679898874741970"
    },
