      "settings": {
        "checksum": "777b243d47b476b8606c215be1544f077689dcef00e3d0daf106b7e5b5751c9b_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg2skFYSnGC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-51bd7b08-f4ec-461e-bc36-e7734dd26e06.jpg",
        "ggBZyLN-waC_text": "<p>Your order today is protected by our iron-clad 90-day <strong>100% money-back guarantee. </strong>If you don't experience the remarkable <strong>relief from back pain and Sciatica</strong> that you were anticipating, or if you're not amazed by how much easier it is to move, then at any time in the next <strong>90 days,</strong> let us know and we will refund every single penny of your investment. <strong>No questions asked.</strong></p>",
