        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>But here’s the truth: real relief isn’t about masking the pain. It’s about helping your body heal - by restoring strength, easing tension, and getting blood flowing where it’s needed most. Because when you solve the root problem, you don't just feel better - you start living better.</p>",
