        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Pain Is Stealing Moments You’ll Never Get Back.",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Every day you spend battling back pain, aching muscles, or stiff joints is a day you’re not living the way you deserve. Pain doesn’t just hurt your body - it wears down your spirit, robs you of energy, and dims the simple joys of life.</p>",
        "ggsYx-iOo9g_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-6d2134f2-b594-4de8-a4c2-9bc7c1c960de.png",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Pain Is Stealing Moments You’ll Never Get Back."
