        "gggjLf4dDUF_text": "<p>FREE SHIPPING</p>",
        "ggnO_gdadKG_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">Every SmoothSpine™ NMES Back Massager is crafted with premium materials, rigorously tested for durability, and backed by clinical science. We stand by our quality - so you can stand taller, move freer, and live better.</span></p>",
