        "gg029TQ7PQT_text": "<p>“I Thought Nothing Would Help My Sciatica - I Was Wrong.”</p>",
        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>“I’m Not Tech-Savvy, But This Was So Easy”</p>",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>“Better Than Painkillers And No Side Effects”</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>\"I was relying on prescription meds to get through my day, but they made me groggy and didn’t address the real issue. I wasn’t sure if a massager could do much, but this NMES device surprised me. It gets deep into the muscles, eases the pain, and I actually feel stronger. I’ve gone a full month now without needing pills.\"</p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>– Susan Wright</p>",
