        "ggZSVoxxXVa_text": "<p>\"I was nervous about using an electronic device - I’m not great with tech and thought it would be confusing. But SmoothSpine made it simple. I just attach it, press a button, and it does the work. It’s helped relieve my stiff lower back and even the spasms I used to wake up with.\"</p>",
        "gg_nv0E1WSj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-c47e54eb-2f08-457c-9d42-d406243a013b.webp",
