        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>– Rachel Thompson</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>\"I’ve tried physical therapy, TENS units, and even considered surgery for my sciatica. Nothing really worked long-term, and I was skeptical this little device would be any different. But after just a week of using the SmoothSpine NMES, I noticed a real shift - less nerve pain, more flexibility, and no more limping by noon. It’s the first thing that’s actually helped.\"</p>",
        "ggrydDXALPH_text": "Real Users, Real Life-Changing Results",
        "ggx_FgcD6ei_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-27c91fbe-6163-490e-8d9a-a27998ecbd4d.png"
